---
---
<section class="company" id="company">
  <div class="wrap--tight">
    <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal>The company</span>
    <p class="company__manifesto">
      <span data-reveal style="--rd:0">Lelit Logistics is an independent Amazon Delivery Service Partner —</span>
      <span data-reveal style="--rd:1">built by operators who came up through the cab, dispatch, and fleet.</span>
      <span data-reveal style="--rd:2" class="dim">We own the routes, the vans, and the standard our customers see at the door.</span>
    </p>
    <div class="company__cols">
      <p data-reveal style="--rd:3">
        Founded in 2026 and operating out of Station DOB7 in Glastonbury,
        Connecticut, we know what a good day on the road actually takes —
        because we've driven it ourselves.
      </p>
      <p data-reveal style="--rd:4">
        We invest in training, route planning, and the technology that keeps
        every driver safe and every delivery accounted for. Small fleet.
        Big-fleet discipline.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .company { padding-block: clamp(5rem, 11vw, 9rem); background: var(--bg); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .company__manifesto {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 590; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1.22;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 var(--s8);
  }
  .company__manifesto span { display: block; }
  .company__manifesto .dim { color: var(--gray); }
  .company__cols {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--s6);
    font-size: 16.5px; line-height: 1.65;
  }
  @media (max-width: 720px) { .company__cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--s3); } }
</style>
